# Installation Notes

- XAMPP already installed from previous assignments.
- Started Apache and MySQL.
- Downloaded Dolibarr stable package.
- Placed Dolibarr files in `C:\xampp\htdocs\dolibarr`.
- Created database named `dolibarr` in phpMyAdmin.
- Used local URL `http://localhost/dolibarr/htdocs/install`.
- Set documents directory to `C:\xampp\dolibarr_documents`.
- Created `install.lock` after installation.
